WOOD ELF
Ability Score Increase: WIS +1
Elf Weapon Training: proficiency with longsword, shortsword, shortbow, and longbow.
Fleet of Foot: Base walking speed 35
Mask of Wild: You can try to hide even when only lightly obscured by foliage, heavy rain, falling snow, mist, or other natural phenomena. 


DARK ELF
Ability Score Increase: CHA +1
Superior Darkvision: Darkvision radius =120ft
Sunlight Sensitivity: disadvantage on attack rolls and on WIS (Perception) checks that rely on sight when you, the target of your attack, or whatever you are trying to perceive is in direct sunlight. 
Drow Magic: know the dancing lights cantrip. When reach 3rd level you can cast faerie fire once per day. Once 5th level you can cast darkness spell once per day. Charisma is spellcasting ability for the spells.
Drow Weapon Training: Proficiency with rapiers, shortsword, and hand crossbows. 
